text: Antal Gáborfi (born 1904, date of death unknown) was a Hungarian swimmer. He competed in the men's 100 metre freestyle event at the 1928 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1904 births Category:Year of death missing Category:Hungarian male swimmers Category:Olympic swimmers of Hungary Category:Swimmers at the 1928 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Budapest
